      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example is a true driver\u2019s spec with a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure valvetrain longevity. The chassis has been bolstered with a subframe reinforcement kit, mitigating the platform's known torsional stress points. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, preserving the communicative steering and neutral handling balance this chassis is famous for. A high-performance icon ready for the apex.",
